dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Bayfield County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represent hydrography for Bayfield County in 2019, and includes the layers 'BAYFIELD_HYDRO_2000_LINE' and 'BAYFIELD_HYDRO_2000_POLY'.[This layer contains lake data published by the WI Department of Natural Resources (DNR).Link to metadata information: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/437/GIS-Metadata]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.bayfieldcounty.org/892/GIS-Data-Downloada
